1.1.name: wordpress/wp-post-tips
1.1.description: This is a simple, lightweight plugin that adds tooltips to your 'links' widget using jQuery. The tooltips appear with a bubble image and the description of the link. please leave your comments if you have any suggestions for enhancement.
